sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 로그인 회원
    participant JSP as mypage/reserve.jsp
    participant C as MypageReserveController
    participant S as MypageReserveServiceImpl
    participant M as MypageReserveMapper
    participant DB as Oracle

    User->>JSP: 예약 내역 메뉴
    JSP->>C: GET /mypage/reserve?status=
    C->>C: session memberNo 확인
    C->>S: getMyReservationList(memberNo, status)
    S->>M: selectMyReservations
    M->>DB: SELECT TB_RESERVATION JOIN
    C-->>JSP: reservationList 렌더링
